%3A%2F%2FYahoo.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYahoo.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Yahoo%20News%2C%20Yahoo%20Mail%2C%20and%20Yahoo%20Search.%20In%202025%2C%20he%20says%2C%20Yahoo%20is%20thinking%20about%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20draw%20from%20the%20past%20and%20all%20the%20great%20things%20that%20people%20relied%20on%20Yahoo%20for%2030%20years%2C%20but%20how%20do%20you%20also%20start%20to%20layer%20on%20AI%20and%20all%20these%20other%20capabilities%20that%20start%20to%20supercharge%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENostalgia%20for%20certain%20jeans%20in%20the%20ever-cyclical%20fashion%20industry%20is%20one%20thing%3B%20nostalgia%20for%20a%20more%20wholesome%20internet%20in%20the%20ever-accelerating%20tech%20industry%20is%20another.%20Ultimately%2C%20Yahoo%20will%20need%20more%20than%20memories%20of%20better%20days%20on%20the%20interwebs%20to%20keep%20people%20hanging%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20this%20%26quot%3Bmodern-vintage%26quot%3B%20strategy%20seems%20to%20be%20working%20for%20Yahoo.%20For%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20emails%20with%20an%20%40yahoo%20domain%20have%20raised%20eyebrows.%20But%20after%20revamping%20Yahoo%20Mail%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20125%25%20increase%20in%20new%20users%20connecting%20their%20Gmail%20accounts%20to%20Yahoo%20Mail%20on%20their%20desktops.%20The%20number%20of%20Yahoo%20Mail%20monthly%20active%20users%20on%20iOS%20has%20been%20growing%20by%20double%20digits%20year%20over%20year%20for%20the%20past%20several%20months.%20Traffic%20on%20Yahoo%20News%20on%20mobile%20is%20up%2010%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Comscore%20data%20provided%20by%20Yahoo%2C%20and%20Similarweb%20ranks%20Yahoo%20as%20the%20top%20news%20and%20media%20destination%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYahoo%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20companies%20to%20survive%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20and%20continue%20to%20thrive.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20internet%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20place%20where%20you%20could%20freely%20make%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Amanda%20Brennan%2C%20an%20internet%20librarian%20who%20worked%20as%20Tumblr's%20head%20of%20content%20until%202021.%20People%20in%20their%2030s%20and%20up%20feel%20%26quot%3Bnostalgia%20for%20this%20internet%20that%20didn't%20have%20all%20this%20heaviness%26quot%3B%20and%20where%20more%20anonymous%20interactions%20dominated%20over%20virality%20and%20cancel%20culture%2C%20she%20adds.%20With%20its%20campaign%2C%20Yahoo%20is%20also%20reaching%20younger%20people%20and%20%26quot%3Bselling%20the%20idea%20of%20what%20the%20internet%20was%20to%20people%20who%20cannot%20grasp%20the%20idea%20of%20what%20actually%20existed%2C%26quot%3B%20Brennan%20says.%20As%20people%20are%20increasingly%20interested%20in%20setting%20boundaries%20around%20their%20social%20media%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcure-for-doomscrolling-shaming-your-friends-screentime-app-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Escreen%20time%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Yahoo%20is%20playing%20up%20the%20good%20old%20days%20with%20its%20fun%2C%20purple%2C%20cartoonish%20design%20scheme%20on%20its%20site%20and%20app%2C%20and%20some%20webpages%20load%20with%20an%20oversize%20cursor%20reminiscent%20of%20early%20browsing%20designs.%20On%20Yahoo's%20info%20page%2C%20the%20company%20touts%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20nice%20place%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECultural%20monoliths%20are%20disappearing%20as%20the%20media%20landscape%20fractures.%20In%20calling%20back%20tech's%20early%20days%2C%20the%20company%20is%20leveraging%20a%20rare%20%26quot%3Bconnection%20point%20for%20multiple%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Juan%20Pellerano-Rend%C3%B3n%2C%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20the%20e-commerce-software%20company%20Swap.%20By%20referencing%20a%20more%20adored%20internet%20of%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20the%20company%20is%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20Gen%20Z%2C%20look%20at%20this%20cool%20thing.%20And%20hey%2C%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20X%2C%20remember%20this%20old%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20effective%3A%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Gen%20Z%20users%20didn't%20come%20online%20until%20after%20Google%20had%20become%20synonymous%20with%20search%2C%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%20combined%20make%20up%20more%20than%2045%25%20of%20visitors%20to%20Yahoo%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Yahoo%20Finance%20is%20the%20top%20destination%20for%20financial%20information%20among%20the%20two%20generations%2C%20Comscore%20data%20provided%20by%20Yahoo%20shows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20other%20brands%20have%20been%20deploying%20this%20tactic.%20UScellular%20last%20year%20put%20out%20an%20ad%20featuring%20Alanis%20Morissette%20that%20played%20on%20her%20hit%20song%20%26quot%3BIronic%26quot%3B%20and%20focused%20on%20using%20phones%20less%3B%20Levi's%20got%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20to%20recreate%20an%20ad%20spot%20from%20the%201980s.%20This%20nostalgia-washing%20could%20be%20great%20for%20engagement%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20fleeting%20microtrend%2C%20particularly%20in%20tech%2C%20Pellerano-Rend%C3%B3n%20says%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20long-term%20brand-ethos%20strategy.%20If%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20your%20brand%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20past%20and%20that's%20what's%20bringing%20people%20in%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20investors%20are%20going%20to%20stand%20behind%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20brands%26quot%3B%20if%20that's%20all%20they%20have%20going%2C%20he%20says.%20While%20we%20may%20long%20for%20the%20days%20of%20a%20more%20freewheeling%20internet%2C%20that's%20not%20what%20pays%20the%20bills%20for%20Big%20Tech.%20People%20may%20buy%20old%2C%20colorful%20iPod%20Nanos%20and%20Shuffles%2C%20Apple%20isn't%20leaning%20heavily%20back%20into%20the%20products.%20The%20relaunch%20of%20the%20Motorola%20Razr%20generated%20viral%20hype%2C%20but%20you%20probably%20don't%20know%20anyone%20who%20bought%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20said%2C%20Yahoo's%20strategy%20has%20another%20thing%20going%20for%20it%3A%20backlash%20against%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Yahoo%20has%20tried%20to%20take%20back%20its%20cool.%20In%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20Yahoo%20redid%20its%20logo%20to%20be%20what%20then-CEO%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyahoo-marissa-mayer-rise-and-fall-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EMarissa%20Mayer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20%26quot%3Bwhimsical%2C%20yet%20sophisticated.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20made%20several%20big%20swings%20that%20ultimately%20fizzled%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-yahoo-ceo-mayer-admitted-company-should-have-bought-netflix-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EYahoo%20bought%20Tumblr%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20%241%20billion%20and%20tried%20to%20get%20into%20streaming%20with%20Yahoo%20Screen.%20But%20a%20series%20of%20high-profile%20missteps%20caught%20up%20with%20the%20company.%20In%20its%20early%20years%2C%20Yahoo%20passed%20up%20a%20chance%20to%20buy%20Google%20and%20missed%20a%20shot%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mark-zuckerberg-turned-down-yahoos-1-billion-offer-to-buy-facebook-in-2006-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Eacquire%20Facebook%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20deals%20that%20would%20have%20cost%20pennies%20on%20the%20dollar%20compared%20with%20what%20those%20companies%20are%20now%20worth.%20In%202013%2C%20all%203%20billion%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyahoo-3-billion-accounts-were-compromised-in-its-hacking-attack-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EYahoo%20accounts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20hit%20by%20a%20security%20breach.%20The%20company%20was%20too%20late%20to%20adapt%20to%20mobile%2C%20a%20move%20that%20some%20declared%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20Yahoo.%20In%202016%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverizon-acquires-yahoo-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EVerizon%20bought%20Yahoo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20less%20than%20%245%20billion%20and%20took%20it%20private.%20In%202021%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverizon-sells-aol-yahoo-to-apollo-global-management-5-billion-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EYahoo%20was%20bought%20by%20the%20private-equity%20firm%20Apollo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20By%20then%2C%20Yahoo's%20relevance%20had%20long%20been%20eclipsed%20by%20Meta%20and%20Google.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20now%20it's%20Meta%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-layoffs-innovation-boring-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EGoogle%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20several%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20that%20are%20losing%20their%20cool.%20Meta's%20big%20bid%20to%20transform%20the%20social%20web%20into%20the%20metaverse%20has%20flopped%2C%20leaving%20the%20company%20to%20scramble%20in%20pivots%20toward%20glasses%20as%20the%20future%20of%20computing.%20Google's%20push%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20AI%20realm%20has%20led%20the%20company%20to%20torpedo%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Ftimmytimmytimmytim.bsky.social%2Fpost%2F3lfupj5dnbs24%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Esearch%20results%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20favor%20of%20telling%20people%20to%20put%20glue%20on%20pizza%20or%20that%20water%20will%20freeze%20at%2032%20degrees%20but%20not%2027.%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20remade%20Twitter%20in%20his%20image.%20Apple%20added%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefurbished-iphones-market-apple-sales-slump-android-cell-phones-cheaper-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20to%20its%20iPhone%2016%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20met%20with%20a%20shrug%20from%20consumers.%20As%20all%20these%20companies%20push%20for%20the%20future%2C%20Yahoo%20is%20marketing%20itself%20as%20a%20relic%20of%20a%20time%20when%20the%20internet%20was%20fun%20and%20full%20of%20opportunities%20for%20discovery%20but%20also%20signaling%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20generative-AI%20future.%20That's%20its%20challenge%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20very%20fragmented%20world%20where%20the%20algorithms%20maybe%20pushed%20everyone%20deeper%20into%20the%20things%20that%20they're%20reacting%20to%20most%2C%20how%20do%20you%20bring%20back%20the%20best%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20find%20those%20serendipitous%20or%20delightful%20moments%20mixed%20in%20with%20the%20stuff%20that%20we%20know%20you%20need%20to%20know%20or%20we%20know%20are%20going%20to%20help%20you%20accomplish%20your%20goals%20today%3F%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20pioneering%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20Yahoo%20became%20a%20media%20company%20more%20than%20a%20tech%20company.%20While%20everyone%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20building%20their%20own%20AI%2C%20Yahoo's%20approach%20is%20different.%20Its%20tools%20are%20built%20on%20large%20language%20models%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Google%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20open-source%20LLMs%2C%20Sanchez%20tells%20me%2C%20while%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20even%20Musk's%20xAI%20are%20building%20LLMs.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bsupercharge%26quot%3B%20Yahoo's%20functions%2C%20he%20says%2C%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20summarize%20sporting%20events%20or%20organize%20unwieldy%20inboxes.%20That%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20to%20the%20company.%20%26quot%3BYahoo%20can%20be%20cool%20by%20making%20its%20search%20engine%20more%20conversational%2C%20assistive%2C%20and%20agentic%2C%26quot%3B%20Nikhil%20Lai%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Forrester%20Research%2C%20says%20in%20an%20email.%20More%20than%20one-third%20of%20people%20are%20using%20these%20conversational%20features%20to%20search%20%26quot%3Bwhenever%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Lai%20says%2C%20citing%20data%20from%20Forrester's%20Market%20Research%20Online%20Community.%20In%20addition%20to%20traditional%20search%2C%20Yahoo's%20search%20has%20an%20AI-powered%20chatbot%20designed%20to%20work%20much%20like%20ChatGPT%20or%20Perplexity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20date%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20myself%2C%20I%20probably%20last%20used%20my%20Yahoo%20email%20to%20apply%20to%20colleges%20in%202012%2C%20and%20it's%20since%20become%20a%20repository%20for%20promotional%20emails%20from%20companies%20I%20rarely%20shop%20from.%20For%20all%20the%20nostalgia%20Yahoo%20is%20playing%20up%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20company%20moving%20to%20add%20AI%20into%20its%20various%20apps%2C%20tech%20that%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20hype%20with%20yet-to-be-realized%20returns.%20The%20nudges%20to%20the%20'90s%20don't%20mean%20the%20company%20is%20actually%20moving%20backward%20to%20a%20young%20internet%20many%20long%20for.%20Those%20who%20come%20for%20the%20memories%20are%20going%20to%20find%20a%20very%20different%20Yahoo%20from%20the%20one%20they%20remember%20from%202005.%20But%20in%20the%20Big%20Tech%20landscape%20of%202025%2C%20Yahoo%20might%20not%20need%20to%20be%20cool%20to%20succeed%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20needs%20to%20be%20useful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3