%20-%20DeepSeek%20V3%2C%20a%20671%20billion%20parameter%2C%20'mixture%20of%20experts'%20model%3B%20and%20DeepSeek%20R1%2C%20an%20advanced%20reasoning%20model%20that%20uses%20AI%2C%20possibly%20better%20than%20OpenAI's%2001%20-%20have%20underlined%20its%20status%20as%20a%20potential%20heavyweight%20financial%20and%20technological%20disruptor%20in%20this%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20of%20a%20disruptor%20is%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20this%20app%2C%20the%20DeepSeek%20V3%20model%2C%20is%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fai%2Fchinese-ai-startup-deepseek-overtakes-chatgpt-on-apple-app-store-7568810%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20downloaded%20app%20on%20the%20Apple%20Store%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20let%20that%20sink%20in...%20a%20Chinese-developed%20chatbot%20is%20now%20the%20most-downloaded%20app%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20disruption%2C%20even%20if%20seen%20as%20a%20'potential'%20one%20at%20this%20time%2C%20has%20raised%20doubts%20about%20how%20well%20some%20US%20tech%20companies%20have%20invested%20the%20billions%20pledged%20towards%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20cost%20efficiency%20of%20DeepSeek's%20models%20have%20flipped%20this%20narrative%3B%20even%20if%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20this%20particular%20Chinese%20model%20flops%2C%20that%20it%20was%20developed%20with%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20financial%20and%20technological%20resources%20available%20to%20firms%20in%20the%20West%20is%20an%20eye-opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20how%20much%20of%20a%20disruptor%20is%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20last%20month%20DeepSeek's%20creators%20said%20%3Cstrong%3Etraining%20the%20V3%20model%20required%20less%20than%20%246%20million%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(although%20critics%20say%20the%20addition%20of%20costs%20from%20earlier%20development%20stages%20could%20push%20eventual%20costs%20north%20of%20%241%20billion)%20in%20computing%20power%20from%20Nvidia's%20H800%20chips.%20%26quot%3BDid%20DeepSeek%20really%20build%20OpenAI%20for%20%245%20million%3F%20Of%20course%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%20analyst%20Stacy%20Rasgon%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20break%20down%20the%20available%20financials%20and%20it%20gets%20quite%20remarkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%2001%20charges%20%2415%20per%20million%20input%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20R1%20charges%20%24.55%20per%20million%20input%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pricing%2C%20therefore%2C%20absolutely%20blows%20the%20competition%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20depending%20on%20end-use%20cases%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EDeepSeek%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20between%2020%20and%2050%20times%20more%20affordable%2C%20and%20efficient%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20than%20OpenAI's%2001%20model.%20In%20fact%2C%20logical%20reasoning%20test%20score%20results%20are%20staggering%3B%20DeepSeek%20outperforms%20ChatGPT%20and%20Claude%20AI%20by%20seven%20to%2014%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdev.to%2Farpitstack%2Fdeepseek-r1-vs-gpt-the-ai-showdown-thats-changing-everything-35k9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDev.to%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20online%20community%20for%20software%20developers%2C%20said%20it%20scored%2092%20per%20cent%20in%20completing%20complex%2C%20problem-solving%20tasks%2C%20compared%20to%2078%20per%20cent%20by%20GPT-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInput%20tokens%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20refer%20to%20units%20of%20information%20as%20part%20of%20a%20prompt%20or%20question.%20These%20are%20basically%20what%20the%20model%20needs%20to%20analyse%20or%20understand%20the%20context%20of%20a%20query%20or%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20believed%20to%20spend%20%245%20billion%20every%20year%20to%20develop%20its%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20even%20if%20DeepSeek's%20critics%20(see%20above)%20are%20right%2C%20it%20is%20still%20a%20fraction%20of%20OpenAI's%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20translates%2C%20as%20company%20boss%20Sam%20Altman%20pointed%20out%2C%20into%20significantly%20enhanced%20computing%20capabilities%2C%20but%20for%20the%20DeepSeek%20model%20to%20deliver%20at%20least%20that%20much%20processing%20power%20on%20its%20relatively%20shoestring%20budget%20is%20an%20eyebrow-raiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Mr%20Altman%20acknowledged%20that%2C%20calling%20the%20R1%20model%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impressive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20boss%20Sundar%20Pichai%20went%20one%20step%20further%2C%20telling%20CNBC%20at%20Davos%2C%20%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20we%20should%20take%20the%20development%20out%20of%20China%2C%20very%2C%20very%20seriously.%26quot%3B%20And%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20sounded%20a%20%26quot%3Bwake-up%26quot%3B%20call%20to%20American%20tech%20and%20computing%20giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20are%20the%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20that%20US%20companies%20have%20lost%20amid%20a%20rout%20this%20week%20in%20tech%20stocks%3B%20chip-maker%20Nvidia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20lost%20over%20%24600%20billion%20and%20the%20tech-rich%20Nasdaq%20index%20finished%20Monday%20down%20by%20more%20than%20three%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20the%20unwelcome%20possibility%20of%20a%20further%20drop%20based%20on%20AI%20giants%20Meta%20and%20Microsoft's%20expected%20earnings%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20Meta%20and%20Microsoft%20both%20have%20their%20own%20AI%20models%2C%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20which%20are%20Llama%20and%20Copilot%3B%20the%20former%20is%20a%20LLM%20that%20was%20first%20released%20in%20February%202023%20and%20the%20latter%20is%20now%20an%20integrated%20feature%20in%20various%20Microsoft%20365%20applications%2C%20such%20as%20MS%20Word%20and%20Excel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20neither%20is%2C%20arguably%2C%20on%20the%20same%20tech%20level%20as%20OpenAI%20or%20ChatGPT%2C%20Meta%20and%20MS%20have%20invested%20billions%20in%20AI%20and%20LLM%20projects%2C%20both%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20analysts%20believe%20big%20US%20cloud%20companies%20will%20spend%20%24250%20billion%20this%20year%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20makes%20DeepSeek%20special%20is%20more%20than%20the%20cost%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20that%2C%20unlike%20its%20competitors%2C%20it%20is%20genuinely%20open-source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3ER1%20code%20is%20completely%20open%20to%20the%20public%20under%20the%20MIT%20License%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20permissive%20software%20license%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20use%2C%20modify%2C%20and%20distribute%20software%20with%20few%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20you%20can%20download%20it%2C%20use%20it%20commercially%20without%20fees%2C%20change%20its%20architecture%2C%20and%20integrate%20it%20into%20any%20of%20your%20existing%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20is%20also%20faster%20than%20GPT%204%2C%20more%20practical%20and%2C%20according%20to%20many%20experts%2C%20even%20understands%20regional%20idioms%20and%20cultural%20contexts%20better%20than%20its%20Western%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20much%20more%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%2C%20for%20example%2C%20does%20DeepSeek%20affect%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20ties%20between%20China%20and%20the%20US%20(and%20India%20also%2C%20actually)%2C%20and%20what%20are%20the%20ethical%20problems%20with%20truly%20open-source%20AI%20models%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20undeniable%20is%20that%20China's%20DeepSeek%20is%20a%20disruptor%2C%20in%20financial%20and%20tech%20terms.%20And%20experts%20believe%20China%20has%20now%20leapfrogged%20-%20from%2018%20to%20six%20months%20behind%20state-of-the-art%20AI%20models%20developed%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2