dependence%20show%20his%20narrow%20mindset.%20In%20his%20hunger%20for%20power%2C%20he%20has%20forgotten%20that%20these%20royal%20families%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20equality%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia%20said%20Baroda%20king%20Sayajirao%20Gaekwad%20helped%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20financially%20so%20that%20he%20could%20pursue%20education.%20%26quot%3BShahuji%20Maharaj%20provided%2050%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20backward%20classes%20in%20his%20administration%20in%201902%2C%20laying%20the%20foundation%20of%20social%20justice.%20Gwalior's%20Madhav%20Maharaj%20I%20set%20up%20centres%20of%20education%20and%20jobs%20to%20empower%20backward%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20was%20among%20the%20leaders%20close%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20said%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20gave%20birth%20to%20the%20tyrannical%20mindset%20that%20attacked%20the%20rights%20of%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%2C%20first%20study%20history%2C%20then%20give%20speeches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive-time%20MP%20Dushyant%20Singh%2C%20whose%20mother%20and%20BJP%20veteran%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20is%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia's%20aunt%2C%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20are%20an%20example%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Breckless%20'hit-and-run'%20politics%2C%20where%20he%20makes%20sweeping%20generalisations%20without%20understanding%20history%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BClaiming%20that%20royal%20families%20did%20nothing%20for%20the%20poor%20shows%20ignorance%20of%20the%20immense%20contributions%20made%20by%20leaders%20like%20Shahu%20Maharaj%20of%20Kolhapur%2C%20who%20championed%20social%20reforms%2C%20and%20the%20Gaekwad%20family%20of%20Vadodara%2C%20who%20supported%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar's%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dholpur%20royals%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20social%20and%20infrastructural%20development.%20Maharaj%20Rana%20Nihal%20Singh%20modernised%20the%20state's%20administration%2C%20built%20hospitals%2C%20and%20developed%20essential%20public%20infrastructure%20like%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20while%20his%20successor%20continued%20these%20progressive%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Dholpur%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20families%20played%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20shaping%20India's%20progress%20toward%20equality%20and%20justice.%20Dismissing%20their%20efforts%20not%20only%20disrespects%20their%20legacy%20but%20also%20exposes%20Rahul's%20habit%20of%20making%20baseless%20comments%20for%20political%20mileage.%20Instead%20of%20undermining%20history%2C%20he%20should%20focus%20on%20substantive%20solutions%20to%20current%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20royal%20charge%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20good%20deeds%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20royals%20do%20not%20eclipse%20the%20majority's%20bad%20deeds.%20Targeting%20Mr%20Scindia%2C%20he%20said%20if%20the%20Constitution%20was%20not%20amended%2C%20the%20Gwalior%20dynasty%20would%20still%20be%20drawing%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20tax-free%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20as%20they%20did%20till%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Scindia's%20royal%20lineage%2C%20Mr%20Khera%20quoted%20Subhadra%20Kumari%20Chauhan's%20poem%2C%20Khub%20Ladi%20Mardani%20Woh%20Toh%20Jhansi%20Wali%20Rani%20Thi%2C%20which%20remembers%20Queen%20Lakshmibai's%20bravery%20during%20the%20First%20War%20of%20Independence%20in%201857.%20The%20lines%20recount%20that%20the%20ruler%20of%20the%20Scindia%20dynasty%2C%20who%20sided%20with%20the%20British%20during%20the%201857%20revolt%2C%20had%20fled%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia's%20political%20rivals%20have%20often%20used%20the%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20jab%20against%20him%20by%20citing%20Gwalior%20ruler%20Jayakirao%20Scindi