%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738043940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F381kv14g_deepseek-_625x300_28_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinas-deepseek-evades-questions-on-arunachal-pradesh-sorry-thats-beyond-7576343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20exchange%20has%20sparked%20interest%20and%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20chatbot's%20programming%20and%20potential%20biases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinas-deepseek-evades-questions-on-arunachal-pradesh-sorry-thats-beyond-7576343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Lost%2C%20Who%20Won%20After%20Selloff%20Linked%20To%20DeepSeek%20Slams%20Markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20500%20richest%20people%2C%20led%20by%20Nvidia%20Corp.%20co-founder%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20lost%20a%20combined%20%24108%20billion%20on%20Monday%20as%20a%20tech-led%20selloff%20tied%20to%20Chinese%20AI%20developer%20DeepSeek%20sent%20major%20indices%20plunging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBillionaires%20whose%20fortunes%20are%20linked%20to%20artificial%20intelligence%20were%20the%20biggest%20losers%3A%20Huang%20saw%20his%20fortune%20fall%20%2420.1%20billion%2C%20a%2020%25%20drop%2C%20while%20Oracle%20Corp.%20co-founder%20Larry%20Ellison's%20%2422.6%20billion%20loss%20was%20larger%20in%20absolute%20terms%2C%20but%20represented%20just%2012%25%20of%20his%20fortune%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index.%20Dell%20Inc.'s%20Michael%20Dell%20lost%20%2413%20billion%2C%20and%20Binance%20Holdings%20Ltd.%20co-founder%20Changpeng%20%26quot%3BCZ%26quot%3B%20Zhao%20shaved%20%2412.1%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETech-sector%20titans%20as%20a%20group%20saw%20%2494%20billion%20of%20wealth%20evaporate%20-%20roughly%2085%25%20of%20the%20Bloomberg%20index's%20total%20decline.%20The%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20Index%20fell%203.1%25%2C%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20dropped%201.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHangzhou-based%20DeepSeek%20has%20been%20developing%20AI%20models%20since%202023%2C%20but%20the%20company%20first%20came%20onto%20the%20radar%20of%20many%20Western%20investors%20this%20weekend%20as%20its%20free%20DeepSeek%20R1%20chatbot%20app%20topped%20download%20charts%20worldwide.%20So%20many%20new%20users%20piled%20in%20that%20DeepSeek%20struggled%20to%20keep%20the%20app%20online%2C%20suffering%20outages%20and%20forcing%20it%20to%20restrict%20signups%20to%20users%20with%20Chinese%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20dark-horse%20entry%20into%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20which%20it%20says%20cost%20just%20%245.6%20million%20to%20develop%2C%20is%20a%20challenge%20to%20Silicon%20Valley's%20narrative%20that%20massive%20capital%20spending%20is%20essential%20to%20developing%20the%20strongest%20models.%20That%20delivered%20a%20serious%20blow%20to%20billionaires%20whose%20fortunes%20are%20tied%20to%20the%20Western%20AI%20supply%20chain%20that's%20been%20the%20equities%20market's%20biggest%20driver%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimilar%20Playbook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoaring%20valuations%20for%20so-called%20AI%20hyperscalers%20-%20including%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%2C%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20and%20Microsoft%20Corp.%20-%20have%20generated%20billions%20in%20wealth%20for%20their%20owners%20since%20OpenAI%20unveiled%20ChatGPT%20in%20November%202022.%20These%20companies%20have%20for%20the%20most%20part%20operated%20on%20a%20similar%20playbook%3A%20Spend%20huge%20sums%20to%20develop%20and%20run%20AI%20systems%20by%20hoarding%20top-of-the-line%20semiconductors%20and%20the%20energy%20supplies%20needed%20to%20run%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Speakers%20At%20The%20Meta%20Connect%20Event%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20announced%20Friday%20that%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20spend%20%2460%20billion%20to%20%2465%20billion%20on%20projects%20related%20to%20AI%20this%20year%2C%20well%20above%20Wall%20Street%20estimates.%20Capital%20spending%20across%20all%20Big%20Tech%20firms%20is%20on%20pace%20to%20reach%20%24200%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20limited%20revenue%20to%20show%20for%20all%20their%20investment%20so%20far%2C%20markets%20have%20rewarded%20US%20tech%20stocks%20with%20record-high%20valuations%2C%20which%20have%20in%20turn%20generated%20historic%20wealth%20gains%20for%20their%20owners.%20Nvidia%20has%20stood%20out%20as%20the%20AI%20boom's%20biggest%20single%20winner%20so%20far%2C%20with%20Huang's%20net%20worth%20increasing%20almost%20eight-fold%20to%20%24121%20billion%20since%20the%20start%20of%202023%20through%20Friday.%20Zuckerberg's%20fortune%20soared%20385%25%20to%20%24229%20billion%20over%20the%20same%20period%20and%20Amazon.com%20Inc.'s%20Jeff%20Bezos%20gained%20133%25%20to%20%24254%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Huang%20and%20Ellison%20suffered%20losses%2C%20other%20major%20tech%20billionaires'%20fortunes%20escaped%20unscathed.%20Zuckerberg's%20net%20worth%20ended%20the%20day%20up%2C%20gaining%20%244.3%20billion%20as%20Meta%20rebounded%20from%20an%20early-session%20decline.%20Bezos'%20wealth%20climbed%20by%20about%20%24632%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapital%20Spending%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20DeepSeek%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20free%20model%20that%20potentially%20rivals%20or%20beats%20competitors%20including%20ChatGPT%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20development%20cost%20led%20investors%20to%20question%20the%20logic%20behind%20Silicon%20Valley's%20dependence%20on%20capital%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20reason%20why%20DeepSeek%20didn't%20rely%20on%20big%20investment%20and%20top-of-the-line%20chips%20to%20develop%20its%20model%20is%20that%20Chinese%20firms%20have%20had%20limited%20access%20to%20the%20powerful%20GPUs%2C%20or%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20most%20Western%20companies%20rely%20on%20ever%20since%20the%20US%20government%20instituted%20strict%20export%20controls%20on%20the%20most%20advanced%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20last%20week%2C%20Alexandr%20Wang%2C%20CEO%20of%20training%20data%20provider%20Scale%20AI%2C%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20export%20controls%2C%20DeepSeek%20and%20other%20Chinese%20developers%20likely%20have%20more%20GPUs%20than%20Silicon%20Valley%20is%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chinese%20labs%20have%20more%20H100s%20than%20people%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Nvidia's%20top-of-the-line%20AI%20chip.%20%26quot%3BMy%20understanding%20is%20that%20DeepSeek%20has%20about%2050%2C000%20H100s%2C%20which%20they%20can't%20talk%20about%2C%20obviously%2C%20because%20it's%20against%20the%20export%20controls%20that%20the%20US%20has%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738043640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fkci2oii_deepseek-afp_625x300_28_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-lost-who-won-after-selloff-linked-to-deepseek-slams-markets-7576588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20500%20richest%20people%2C%20led%20by%20Nvidia%20Corp.%20co-founder%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20lost%20a%20combined%20%24108%20billion%20on%20Monday%20as%20a%20tech-led%20selloff%20tied%20to%20Chinese%20AI%20developer%20DeepSeek%20sent%20major%20indices%20plunging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-