ues%20including%20security%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Europe.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20telephonic%20conversation%20between%20President%20Trump%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20since%20the%20Republican%20was%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20second%20term%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20that%20PM%20Modi%20was%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20the%20United%20States%20sometime%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20long%20talk%20with%20him%20this%20morning%20(Monday).%20He%20is%20going%20to%20be%20coming%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20over%20next%20month%2C%20probably%20February.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20good%20relationship%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20leader%20noted%20he%20discussed%20the%20issue%20of%20immigration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20and%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20back%20Indian%20immigrants%20who%20came%20to%20the%20US%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20reports%20suggesting%20that%20the%20Indian%20side%20was%20working%20on%20an%20early%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20leaders.%20President%20Trump%20and%20PM%20Modi%20enjoyed%20warm%20relations%20in%20the%20US%20president's%20first%20term%2C%20but%20during%20his%20campaign%20for%20re-election%2C%20the%2078-year-old%20American%20leader%20called%20India%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20big%20abuser%26quot%3B%20of%20trade%20and%20vowed%20to%20use%20tariffs%20on%20global%20imports%20into%20the%20US%20to%20correct%20imbalances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20threatened%20the%20BRICS%20group%20of%20nations%2C%20of%20which%20India%20is%20a%20part%2C%20with%20tariffs%20if%20they%20did%20not%20accept%20his%20demand%20of%20committing%20to%20not%20create%20a%20new%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Trade%20And%20Bilateral%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Monday's%20call%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bemphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20increasing%20its%20procurement%20of%20American-made%20security%20equipment%20and%20moving%20toward%20a%20fair%20bilateral%20trading%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20White%20House%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20two-way%20trade%20surpassed%20%24118%20billion%20in%202023%2F24%2C%20with%20India%20posting%20a%20surplus%20of%20%2432%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20an%20important%20strategic%20partner%20in%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20United%20States%20to%20counter%20China%2C%20and%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20Monday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20called%20Mr%20Trump%20a%20%26quot%3Bdear%20friend%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20and%20trusted%20partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20work%20together%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20our%20people%20and%20towards%20global%20peace%2C%20prosperity%2C%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20statement%20said%20the%20leaders%20discussed%20technology%2C%20trade%2C%20investment%2C%20energy%20and%20defence%20and%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20to%20remain%20in%20touch%20and%20meet%20soon%20at%20an%20early%20mutually%20convenient%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20both%20leaders%20emphasized%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20Quad%20grouping%20that%20brings%20together%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%20with%20Australia%20and%20Japan%2C%20with%20India%20to%20host%20Quad%20leaders%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Immigration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20said%20PM%20Modi%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20back%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%20from%20America.%20In%20a%20meeting%20with%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20last%20week%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20emphasized%20a%20desire%20to%20%26quot%3Baddress%20concerns%20related%20to%20irregular%20migration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20has%20pledged%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20last%20week%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20have%20identified%20some%2018%2C000%20Indian%20migrants%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%20illegally.%20He%20has%20said%20he%20is%20open%20to%20legal%20migration%20of%20skilled%20workers%20and%20India%20is%20known%20for%20its%20massive%20pool%20of%20IT%20professionals%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20work%20across%20the%20world.%20They%20account%20for%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20skilled%20worker%20H-1B%20visas%20issued%20by%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738040760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flag2c5_modi-trump_625x300_06_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-will-do-the-right-thing-donald-trump-on-migrants-row-after-call-with-modi-7576162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Monday%20(local%20time)%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bproductive%26quot%3B%20phone%20call%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20where%20the%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20expanding%20and%20deepening%20cooperation%20and%20issues%20including%20security%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-will-do-the-right-thing-donald-trump-on-migrants-row-after-call-with-modi-7576162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coldplay%20singer%20Chris%20Martin%20%26amp%3B%20Dakota%20Johnson%20reach%20Maha%20Kumbh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe