s%2Fwinter-downpours-trigger-mud-flow-in-fire-ravaged-regions-of-southern-california%2Famp_articleshow%2F117616467.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20Calls%20Himself%20%26quot%3BProduct%26quot%3B%20Of%20India-US%20Bond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20said%20he%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cproduct%20of%20the%20bond%26quot%3B%20that%20exists%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%2C%20as%20top%20government%20officials%20and%20American%20lawmakers%20lauded%20the%20Indian%20community's%20contribution%20during%20Republic%20Day%20commemoration%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Seattle%20hosted%20a%20special%20reception%20on%20Sunday%20at%C2%A0the%20Bell%20Harbour%20Conference%20Centre%20to%20commemorate%20India's%2076th%20Republic%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20State%20Governor%20Bob%20Ferguson%20and%20Mr%20Nadella%20were%20the%20Guests%20of%20Honour%20at%20the%20reception%20attended%20by%20over%20500%20people%20from%20the%20Indian-American%20community%2C%20according%20to%20a%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20Consulate.%C2%A0In%20a%20unique%20first%2C%20several%20members%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20also%20joined%20the%20evening%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadella%2C%20addressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20a%20product%20of%20the%20bond%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20(India%20and%20US).%E2%80%9D%20He%20praised%20the%20leadership%20of%20both%20nations%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfocus%20on%20how%20to%20use%20technology%20to%20leverage%20education%20outcomes%2C%20health%20outcomes%2C%20public%20service%20efficiency%2C%20competitiveness%20and%20productivity%20of%20small%20businesses%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20members%20of%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20reception%2C%20Ferguson%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%2024th%20Gov