ent%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20at%20a%20House%20Republican%20members%20conference%20meeting%20in%20Miami%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Frantz%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20addressed%20the%20rise%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20a%20Chinese%20AI%20app%2C%20on%20Monday%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20the%20ability%20to%20train%20AI%20cheaply%2C%20which%20DeepSeek%20said%20it%20has%20done%2C%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20that%20DeepSeek%20challenges%20the%20idea%20of%20US%20tech%20dominance%2C%20but%20that%20may%20be%20positive%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20Chinese%20AI%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-r1-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ability%20to%20train%20AI%20more%20cheaply%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpositive%26quot%3B%20development%20and%20should%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bwake-up%20call%26quot%3B%20for%20tech%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20comments%20followed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-number-one-app-apple-store-openai-chatgpt-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek's%20ascension%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Apple's%20free%20downloads%20chart%2C%20which%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20US%20tech%20market%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20won't%20be%20spending%20as%20much%2C%20and%20you'll%20get%20the%20same%20result%20hopefully%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20Monday%20evening%20in%20a%20House%20Republican%20members%20conference%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BThe%20release%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20AI%20from%20a%20Chinese%20company%2C%20should%20be%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20our%20industries%20that%20we%20need%20to%20be%20laser-focused%20on%20competing%20to%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20heavily%20investing%20in%20its%20tech%2