3BAs%20AI%20gets%20more%20efficient%20and%20accessible%2C%20we%20will%20see%20its%20use%20skyrocket%2C%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20commodity%20we%20just%20can't%20get%20enough%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20that%20as%20tech%20improves%2C%20whether%20smarter%2C%20cheaper%2C%20or%20both%2C%20it%20will%20only%20bring%20in%20exponentially%20more%20demand%20is%20based%20on%20a%2019th-century%20economic%20principle.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20companies%20looking%20to%20dip%20their%20toe%20into%20AI%20has%20been%20high.%20Cheaper%20tools%20could%20encourage%20more%20experimentation%20and%20further%20the%20technology%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilar%20to%20Llama%2C%20it%20lowers%20the%20barriers%20to%20adoption%2C%20enabling%20more%20businesses%20to%20accelerate%20AI%20use%20cases%20and%20move%20them%20into%20production.%26quot%3B%20Umesh%20Padval%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Thomvest%20Ventures%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20even%20if%20AI%20grows%20faster%20than%20ever%2C%20that%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20the%20trillions%20of%20investments%20that%20have%20flooded%20the%20space%20will%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291d382b3-4ea3-4212-bad1-e5339b75068b%5C%22%3ETake%202%3A%20DeepSeek%20broke%20the%20prevailing%20wisdom%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20seems%20to%20have%20broken%20the%20assumption%20that%20you%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20capital%20to%20train%20cutting-edge%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Debarghya%20Das%2C%20an%20investor%20at%20Menlo%20Ventures%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20DeepSeek's%20open-source%20model%20is%20competitive%20%E2%80%94%2020%20to%2040%20times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ai-lab-deepseek-massively-undercuts-openai-on-pricing-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeaper%20to%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20comparable%20models%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20according%20to%20Bernstein%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20cost%20of%20building%20DeepSeek%20models%20is%20hotly%20debated.%20The%20research%20paper%20from%20DeepSeek%20explaining%20its%20V3%20model%20lists%20a%20training%20cost%20of%20%245.6%20million%20%E2%80%94%20a%20harrowingly%20low%20number%20for%20other%20providers%20of%20foundation%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20same%20paper%20says%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Baforementioned%20costs%20include%20only%20the%20official%20training%20of%20DeepSeek-V3%2C%20excluding%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20prior%20research%20and%20ablation%20experiments%20on%20architectures%2C%20algorithms%2C%20or%20data.%26quot%3B%20So%20the%20%245%20million%20figure%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20ecosystem%20is%20also%20reacting%20strongly%20to%20the%20implication%20that%20DeepSeek's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexplaining-deepseek-chinese-models-efficiency-scaring-markets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate-of-the-art%20model%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20cheaper%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20breakthrough%20slashes%20computational%20demands%2C%20enabling%20lower%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20and%20putting%20pressure%20on%20industry%20titans%20like%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%20to%20justify%20their%20premium%20pricing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenneth%20Lamont%2C%20principal%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20remind%20investors%20that%20with%20early-stage%20technology%2C%20assuming%20the%20winners%20are%20set%20is%20folly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMega-trends%20rarely%20unfold%20as%20expected%2C%20and%20today's%20dominant%20players%20might%20not%20be%20tomorrow's%20winners%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamont%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDmitry%20Shevelenko%2C%20the%20chief%20business%20officer%20at%20Perplexity%2C%20a%20big%20consumer%20of%20compute%20and%20existing%20models%2C%20concurred%20that%20Big%20Tech%20players%20would%20need%20to%20rethink%20their%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20challenges%20the%20margin%20structure%20that%20maybe%20they%20were%20selling%20to%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Shevelenko%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20terms%20of%20accelerating%20the%20development%20of%20these%20technologies%2C%20this%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%20Perplexity%20has%20added%20DeepSeek's%20models%20to%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a484b3f-3f73-46b2-89e2-aaeef7d15c2f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%203%3A%20Considering%20a%20switch%20to%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20several%20platforms%20that%20provide%20AI%20models%20for%20businesses%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroq-nvidia-software-advantage-cuda-moat-challenge-inference-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGroq%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Liquid.AI%20to%20name%20two%20%E2%80%94%20added%20DeepSeek's%20models%20to%20their%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Amazon's%20internal%20Slack%2C%20one%20person%20posted%20a%20meme%20suggesting%20that%20developers%20might%20drop%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20AI%20model%20in%20favor%20of%20DeepSeek's%20offerings.%20The%20post%20included%20an%20image%20of%20the%20Claude%20model%20crossed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFriendship%20ended%20with%20Claude.%20Now%20DeepSeek%20is%20my%20best%20friend.%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20post%20seen%20by%20BI%2C%20which%20got%20more%20than%2060%20emoji%20reactions%20from%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20invested%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20Anthropic.%20The%20cloud%20giant%20also%20provides%20access%20to%20Claude%20models%20via%20its%20Amazon%20Web%20Service%20platform.%20And%20some%20AWS%20customers%20are%20asking%20for%20DeepSeek%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-deepseek-customer-cloud-access-bedrock-stripe-toyota-cisco-workday-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20has%20exclusively%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20always%20listening%20to%20customers%20to%20bring%20the%20latest%20emerging%20and%20popular%20models%20to%20AWS%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20while%20noting%20that%20customers%20can%20access%20some%20DeepSeek-related%20products%20on%20AWS%20right%20now%20through%20tools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-models-bedrock-service-success-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBedrock%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20to%20see%20many%20more%20models%20like%20this%20%E2%80%94%20both%20large%20and%20small%2C%20proprietary%20and%20open-source%20%E2%80%94%20excel%20at%20different%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20why%20the%20majority%20of%20Amazon%20Bedrock%20customers%20use%20multiple%20models%20to%20meet%20their%20unique%20needs%20and%20why%20we%20remain%20focused%20on%20providing%20our%20customers%20with%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20so%20they%20can%20easily%20experiment%20and%20integrate%20the%20best%20models%20for%20their%20specific%20needs%20into%20their%20applications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwitching%20costs%20for%20companies%20creating%20their%20own%20products%20on%20top%20of%20foundation%20models%20are%20relatively%20low%2C%20which%20is%20generating%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20as%20to%20whether%20DeepSeek%20will%20overtake%20other%20models%20from%20Meta%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20or%20OpenAI%20in%20popularity%20with%20enterprises.%20(It's%20already%20number%20one%20in%20Apple's%20app%20store.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%2C%20however%2C%20is%20owned%20by%20Chinese%20hedge%20fund%20High-Flyer%20and%20the%20same%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftik-tok-how-it-changed-everything-ban-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20concerns%20haunting%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20eventually%20apply%20to%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20open-source%20models%20like%20DeepSeek%20present%20exciting%20opportunities%2C%20enterprises%E2%80%94especially%20in%20regulated%20industries%E2%80%94may%20hesitate%20to%20adopt%20Chinese-origin%20models%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20training%20data%20transparency%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Padval%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20concerns%20aside%2C%20the%20software%20companies%20that%20sell%20APIs%20to%20businesses%20have%20been%20adding%20DeepSeek%20throughout%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c5d6924-1bb7-4b84-842d-372cc745db70%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%204%3A%20Infrastructure%20players%20could%20take%20a%20hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInfrastructure-as-a-service%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20Oracle%2C%20Digital%20Ocean%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20could%20be%20in%20a%20precarious%20position%20should%20more%20efficient%20AI%20models%20rule%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20efficiency%20of%20DeepSeek's%20pre%20and%20post%20training%20framework%20(if%20true)%20raises%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20or%20not%20global%20hyperscalers%20and%20governments%2C%20that%20have%20and%20intend%20to%20continue%20to%20invest%20significant%20capex%20dollars%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20may%20pause%20to%20consider%20the%20innovative%20methodologies%20that%20have%20come%20to%20light%20with%20DeepSeek's%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Stifel%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20same%20quantity%20of%20work%20requires%20less%20compute%2C%20those%20selling%20only%20compute%20could%20suffer%2C%20Barclays%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20increased%20uncertainty%2C%20we%20could%20see%20share%20price%20pressure%20amongst%20all%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20Digital%20Ocean%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Oracle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20in%20time%20for%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2536402-6bd3-470d-8770-05d4657919fe%5C%22%3ETake%205%3A%20Scaling%20isn't%20dead%2C%20it's%20just%20moved%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20AI%20luminaries%2C%20including%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20have%20been%20predicting%20a%20big%20shift%20in%20AI%20from%20a%20focus%20on%20training%20to%20a%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-players-startups-ai-inference-driving-prices-down-cheap-workload-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Training%20is%20the%20process%20by%20which%20models%20are%20created%20while%20inference%20is%20the%20type%20of%20computing%20that%20runs%20AI%20models%20and%20related%20tools%20such%20as%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20in%20computing's%20total%20share%20to%20inference%20has%20been%20underway%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20now%2C%20change%20is%20coming%20from%20two%20places.%20First%2C%20more%20AI%20users%20means%20more%20inference%20demand.%20The%20second%20is%20that%20part%20of%20DeepSeek's%20secret%20sauce%20is%20how%20improvement%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20inference%20stage.%20Nvidia%20took%20a%20positive%20spin%2C%20via%20a%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20is%20an%20excellent%20AI%20advancement%20and%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20Test%20Time%20Scaling.%20DeepSeek's%20work%20illustrates%20how%20new%20models%20can%20be%20created%20using%20that%20technique%2C%20leveraging%20widely-available%20models%20and%20compute%20that%20is%20fully%20export%20control%20compliant%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInference%20requires%20significant%20numbers%20of%20NVIDIA%20GPUs%20and%20high-performance%20networking.%20We%20now%20have%20three%20scaling%20laws%3A%20pre-training%20and%20post-training%2C%20which%20continue%2C%20and%20new%20test-time%20scaling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225290c103-993e-4f60-995c-53bdef945537%5C%22%3ETake%206%3A%20Open-source%20changes%20model%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20under-hyped%20part%20of%20DeepSeek's%20innovations%20is%20how%20easy%20it%20will%20now%20be%20to%20take%20any%20AI%20model%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20more%20powerful%20%26quot%3Breasoning%26quot%3B%20model%2C%20according%20to%20Jack%20Clark%2C%20an%20Anthropic%20cofounder%2C%20and%20a%20former%20OpenAI%20employee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimportai.substack.com%2Fp%2Fimport-ai-397-deepseek-means-ai-proliferation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20newsletter%20Import%20AI%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20also%20explained%20that%20some%20AI%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20OpenAI%2C%20have%20been%20hiding%20all%20the%20reasoning%20steps%20that%20their%20latest%20AI%20models%20take.%20DeepSeek's%20models%20show%20all%20these%20intermediate%20%26quot%3Bchains%20of%20thought%26quot%3B%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%20and%20use.%20This%20radically%20changes%20how%20AI%20models%20are%20controlled%2C%20Clark%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20providers%20like%20OpenAI%20had%20previously%20chosen%20to%20obscure%20the%20chains%20of%20thought%20of%20their%20models%2C%20making%20this%20harder%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20now%20an%20open-weight%20model%20floating%20around%20the%20internet%20which%20you%20can%20use%20to%20bootstrap%20any%20other%20sufficiently%20powerful%20base%20model%20into%20being%20an%20AI%20reasoner.%20AI%20capabilities%20worldwide%20just%20took%20a%20one-way%20ratchet%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adbb59ab-aac5-48c9-a4a4-a6d04a69d6fb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%207%3A%20Programmers%20still%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20improved%20by%20using%20novel%20programming%20methods%2C%20which%20Samir%20Kumar%2C%20co-founder%20and%20general%20partner%20at%20VC%20firm%20Touring%20Cap