me%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20key%20initiative%20in%20shaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers.%20Through%20this%20programme%2C%20private%20school%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20identify%20real-world%20challenges%20and%20design%20technological%20solutions%20to%20address%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20example%20comes%20from%20a%20student%20who%20realised%20that%20government%20hospitals%20are%20often%20understaffed%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20cater%20to%20every%20bed.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20observed%20that%20when%20an%20IV%20drip%20was%20missing%20from%20any%20bed%2C%20there%20was%20no%20immediate%20way%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff%20to%20be%20alerted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20inspired%20her%20to%20design%20a%20device%20that%20would%20notify%20the%20central%20monitoring%20unit%20in%20the%20hospital%20room%2C%20whenever%20something%20went%20wrong%20with%20an%20IV%20drip.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20presented%20her%20solution%20to%20the%20dean%20of%20Nair%20Hospital%2C%20he%20was%20so%20impressed%20by%20its%20potential%20that%20he%20expressed%20interest%20in%20customising%20it%20further%20to%20make%20the%20solution%20even%20more%20practical%20and%20effective%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20story%20that%20the%20founder%20shares%20is%20that%20of%20a%20class%2011%20student%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Kathak%20dancer.%20%E2%80%9CRealising%20that%20deaf%20children%20struggle%20to%20connect%20with%20music%2C%20she%20invented%20a%20wristband%20that%20tracks%20sound%20waves%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20vibrations.%20This%20allows%20the%20wearer%20to%20dance%20along%20with%20the%20beats%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20government%20school%20children%2C%20TIS%20has%20launched%20Project%20Udaan%2C%20pathways%20for%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20designed%20for%20students%20of%20classes%205%20to%2012.%20The%20programme%20starts%20by%20layin